鏈》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20171021-hongkong-paper-recycling/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20171021-hongkong-paper-recycling%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m67np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=8d527990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20171021-hongkong-paper-recycling/?utm_medium=copy</a><br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你們知不知從前的病房助理員(公務員)屌到病人PK<br />\n冇家屬茶錢, 病人好自為知了........</span>"},{"pid":"02a5edc849dbd6c10f4c906d4419ab3f680bd53c","tid":1088742,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"典型狗官嚟"},{"pid":"cd9ffd890aa6f5c59c074d58b2b85e6b8346cdf5","tid":1088742,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c861c373e126fb5e4c3c5655cd45734363816b6","tid":1088742,"uid":1550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"715e6231303930b51a610b7b2e982362c47199a9","tid":1088742,"uid":226296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T00:04:29.000Z","msg":"平時班廢老咁抽後生又蛇齋餅糭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現眼報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T01:20:48.000Z","msg":"佢地係衰但係唔好咁講<br />\n今日佢地明日我地<br />\n依啲問題點都要解決"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"幫完佢地咪反口後生一口<br />\n<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"37a2376be52e92913ce941aa4f84ef36cfb2bdea","tid":1088742,"uid":53513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"新制連長俸都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b73d9cff2d5d4c58f0ec697445c8d5a4266e3c","tid":1088742,"uid":236131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"仲要社工底，講師級、教授，咁L樣講野？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCtcigG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht